{"type":"message","id":"694564ec","parentId":"7b19193e","timestamp":"2026-04-28T05:02:54.818Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"⚙️ **Evening Check-in: Monday, April 27th, 2026**\n\nThis check-in is structured for optimal reflection and efficiency. Please populate the sections below for a complete review.\n\n**🌙 EVENING REVIEW:** *(Summary of today's key wins/losses.)*\n**👨‍👩‍👧‍👦 FAMILY:** *(Connection point from today.)*\n**🧭 DISCIPLINE:** *(Area for reflection.)*\n**❤️ GRATITUDE:** *(One specific thing to appreciate.)*\n**🎯 TOMORROW'S FOCUS:** *(The single most important outcome for Tuesday.)*\n**🙏 NIGHT PRAYER/REFLECTION:** *(A concluding thought.)*\n\n**Reflection Check:**\n1. On a scale of 1-10, how well did I lead as a husband, father, and coach today? (Please speak your mind.)\n2. **Practical Adjustment for Tomorrow:** [Provide one concrete, actionable change for Tuesday.]\n\n*Word count target: < 180 words.*"}],"stopReason":"stop","api":"ollama","provider":"ollama","model":"gemma4:e4b","usage":{"input":13574,"output":839,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":14413,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"timestamp":1777352574817}}
